1. On je *pomenuo* svoju baku u svom dnevniku. (He mentioned his grandmother in his diary.)
2. Kada je novinar pitao ministra o toj temi, ministar nije *pomenuo* nikakve detalje. (When the journalist asked the minister about that topic, the minister did not mention any details.)
3. Molim te da mi *pomeneš* ako planiraš da odeš ranije. (Please let me know if you plan to leave earlier.)
4. Nisam siguran da li sam ti već *pomenuo* da idem na put sledeće nedelje. (I'm not sure if I've already mentioned to you that I'm going on a trip next week.)
5. Pre nego što je napustio sobu, on je *pomenuo* da će se vratiti kasnije. (Before leaving the room, he mentioned that he would come back later.)
6. On je *pomenuo* novu knjigu koju je pročitao na svom blogu. (He mentioned a new book he read on his blog.)
7. Na sastanku je direktor *pomenuo* važnost poštovanja rokova. (At the meeting, the director mentioned the importance of meeting deadlines.)
8. Nakon što je neko *pomenuo* njegovo ime, on se oglasio iz publike. (After someone mentioned his name, he spoke up from the audience.)